      ],
      "source": "https://bayportbluepointheritage.org/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Bayport Marina’s history mirrors the town’s growth, evolving from a 19th‑century fishing spot into a modern waterfront hub.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        17,
