      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://touristplaces.guide/top-10-places-to-visit-in-bayport-nature-adventure-and-history/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Freedom Park, founded to promote outdoor activities, hosts seasonal festivals and concerts amid its scenic wetlands.",
